-- Toyota sees 5 percent sales growth in Europe in '08
-- 
-- Mon Sep 10, 2007 2:19pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/09/10/us-toyota-europe-idUSN1036068120070910

 

 FRANKFURT  (Reuters) - Toyota Motor Corp ( 7203.T ) said on Monday it was aiming for a 5 percent sales growth in Europe in 2008. 

 "We forecast around 5 percent growth for combined Toyota and Lexus sales (in Europe) in 2008, with Russia in particular continuing to deliver strong market performance," Tadashi Arashima, president and chief executive of Toyota Europe, said ahead of the Frankfurt auto show.